== Hardware detection ==

To choose the right driver, first detect the used I<sup>2</sup>C controllers. The [[Hardware detection|lspci tool]] can be used for this task:
{{RootCmd|lspci {{!}} grep -i smbus}}

== Installation ==

=== Kernel ===

The following kernel options need to be activated:

{{KernelBox|
Device Drivers  --->
   <*> I2C support  --->
      <*> I2C device interface
      [*] Autoselect pertinent helper modules
         I2C Hardware Bus support  --->

         Select the driver for your I2C controller, e.g.:
            <*> Intel 82801 (ICH/PCH) (i2c-i801)
}}

